{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","symbolKind":"var","roleHeading":"Global Variable","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclusterproperties"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSDictionary"},{"type":"text","text":" object where the key is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSString"},{"type":"text","text":". The dictionary key will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be the feature attribute key. The resulting attribute value is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregated from the clustered points. The dictionary value is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSArray"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consisting of two "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExpression"},{"type":"text","text":" objects."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extern"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOption","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNShapeSource.h@T@MLNShapeSourceOption","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOption"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first object determines how the attribute values are accumulated from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cluster points. It is an "},{"code":"NSExpression","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with an expression function that accepts"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"two or more arguments, such as "},{"code":"sum","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"max","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The arguments should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"featureAccumulated","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the previously defined feature attribute key. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resulting value is assigned to the specified attribute key."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The second ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSExpression","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in the array determines which","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attribute values are accessed from individual features within a cluster.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["let firstExpression = NSExpression(format: \"sum:({$featureAccumulated, sumValue})\")","let secondExpression = NSExpression(forKeyPath: \"magnitude\")","let clusterPropertiesDictionary = [\"sumValue\" : [firstExpression, secondExpression]]","","let options : [MLNShapeSourceOption : Any] = [.clustered : true,","                                           .clusterProperties: clusterPropertiesDictionary]"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This option corresponds to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"clusterProperties","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"source property in the MapLibre Style Spec.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This option only affects point features within an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object; it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is ignored when creating an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOption":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOption","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOption","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoption","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Options for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects."}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOption","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","abstract":[{"text":"Data source for ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"requestQueue","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNShape","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNShape","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","title":"MLNStyle","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy object for the current map style."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNStyle"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSDictionary"},{"type":"text","text":" object where the key is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSString"},{"type":"text","text":". The dictionary key will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be the feature attribute key. The resulting attribute value is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregated from the clustered points. The dictionary value is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSArray"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consisting of two "},{"code":"NSExpression","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" objects."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclusterproperties","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSource"}],"abstract":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSource"}}}